      "chunk_id": "sample_teacher_assistant_chunk_0",
      "document_id": "sample_teacher_assistant",
      "document_title": "sample_teacher_assistant",
      "chunk_text": "Smart Teacher Assistant is an AI-powered backend for education workflows.\n\nThe application provides agent endpoints for summarizing documents, creating slide decks, and generating quizzes.\n\nThe chat endpoint answers questions using retrieved document context. It should only answer from indexed documents and say \"Not found in document\" when the answer is missing from the context.\n\nThe retrieval flow indexes local files from the knowledge base folder, splits them into chunks, stores embeddings in a local JSON vector store, and returns the most relevant chunks for a user question.",
